'''增程器'''是一种通過[[燃料|燃料]]驅動的[[輔助動力系統|輔助動力系統]]，用於[[純電動車|純電動車]]上，增程器能讓[[发电机|发电机]]为[[純電動車|純電動車]]的电池充电来延长車輛的行驶里程。这种車輛發動模式會被視為[[混合動力車輛驅動裝置|混合動力]]。最常用的增程器是[[内燃机|内燃机]]<ref>{{Cite web|title=Hybrid vehicle range extenders: goodbye pistons|url=http://www.idtechex.com/research/articles/hybrid-vehicle-range-extenders-goodbye-pistons-00007552.asp?donotredirect=true|accessdate=2015-05-18|author=Harrop|date=2015-03-13|first=Peter|work=IDTechEx|archive-date=2017-09-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170914151606/http://www.idtechex.com/research/articles/hybrid-vehicle-range-extenders-goodbye-pistons-00007552.asp?donotredirect=true}}</ref>。附帶增程器的電動車又被稱為'''增程式电动汽车'''或'''增程式电动车<ref name="BEVx">{{Cite web|title=2014 BMW i3 Electric Car: Why California Set Range Requirements, Engine Limits|url=http://www.greencarreports.com/news/1087888_2014-bmw-i3-electric-car-why-california-set-range-requirements-engine-limits|accessdate=2014-01-19|author=John Voelcker|date=2013-10-23|publisher=Green Car Reports|archive-date=2021-01-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210126213424/https://www.greencarreports.com/news/1087888_2014-bmw-i3-electric-car-why-california-set-range-requirements-engine-limits}}</ref>'''。

